11
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,940
[Episode 20]

12
00:01:27,940 --> 00:01:29,940
[Haitang House]

13
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:32,240
Yi, you came back after so long.

14
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,880
Are you still used to it?

15
00:01:37,110 --> 00:01:38,240
Everything at home

16
00:01:38,550 --> 00:01:39,550
is so familiar,

17
00:01:39,550 --> 00:01:40,550
as if I've never left home.

18
00:01:41,750 --> 00:01:42,720
But when I think about it,

19
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:45,000
I've been married
and living away for years.

20
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:46,470
Yi.

21
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,670
Since you're already back,

22
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,640
you shouldn't be upset

23
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,310
over your unfortunate relationship.

24
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,310
I just don't understand

25
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:56,830
how I was wrong about him.

26
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,390
He had always been

27
00:01:59,550 --> 00:02:01,030
a modest gentleman
ever since our first encounter.

28
00:02:01,830 --> 00:02:03,390
We spent so many years living together.

29
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,830
I only managed to see his true colors

30
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,270
at the end of our marriage.

31
00:02:09,669 --> 00:02:10,800
That's not your fault.

32
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,550
He deceived everyone.

33
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,080
All of us were responsible.

34
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:15,800
If any of us

35
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,870
could detect

36
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,110
what was going to come,

37
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:20,150
you wouldn't need

38
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,800
to go through such a trial.

39
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:25,240
However, I don't regret it.

40
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,590
Really?

41
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,200
But why?

42
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:32,270
It's because we were in love before.

43
00:02:34,270 --> 00:02:35,040
Back then,

44
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,040
he was the man I held dear.

45
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:38,640
He had a gentle glow, like the moon.

46
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,040
Though things turned out this way,

47
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,480
and I see him

48
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:47,390
for who he is now,

49
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:48,390
I

50
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:49,670
still remember

51
00:02:49,670 --> 00:02:51,040
those amazing moments we shared.

52
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:51,920
Isn't that enough?

53
00:02:52,829 --> 00:02:54,079
But the ending

54
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:55,640
isn't good.

55
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,590
For certain things,

56
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,270
we should focus on
more than their endings.

57
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:02,960
If so...

58
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,240
If so, do you think
it's worth giving it a try

59
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:08,990
even though one is destined
to part from their beloved?

60
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:13,590
Si, when you were saying that,

61
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:15,200
were you thinking of

62
00:03:15,550 --> 00:03:16,640
Commandant Yu?

63
00:03:19,829 --> 00:03:20,960
Yi, you caught me again.

64
00:03:21,270 --> 00:03:22,520
True feelings

65
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:24,040
always find a way out.

66
00:03:25,390 --> 00:03:27,640
I realized that you fell for him

67
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:28,990
when we were in Lingshui.

68
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,240
And he has fallen

69
00:03:32,670 --> 00:03:33,640
even deeper for you.

70
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,390
Is that so?

71
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,320
Do you really think

72
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,960
that Commandant Yu
is concerned about me?

73
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,760
One cannot see the truth
within a situation

74
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:44,079
simply because they are within it.

75
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,470
Greetings, My Lord.

76
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:33,270
I'm Cui Xu,
Bulwark General of the State.

77
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:35,230
I'm also the commander
of the Imperial Insignia Guards.

78
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,710
From today onward, you all will be

79
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,440
a part of the Imperial Insignia Guards.

80
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:41,760
You all must be diligent and dutiful,

81
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:43,350
and do your best

82
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:44,909
to protect His Majesty,

83
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:46,000
our city,

84
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,710
and the state of Zhou!

85
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,230
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

86
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:53,580
[Border of Ling'an]

87
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:01,010
[Count of Dongping's Mansion]

88
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:01,470
Excellent.

89
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,760
It's good to have you back.

90
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,000
I'm glad.

91
00:05:07,350 --> 00:05:08,710
I've missed you so much.

92
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:14,350
How about you two chat for a bit?

93
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,200
I'll prepare a feast.

94
00:05:16,470 --> 00:05:17,710
Let's enjoy ourselves

95
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,640
tonight.

96
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:21,000
Thank you, Father.

97
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,470
Pei, you're back after a long journey.

98
00:05:25,470 --> 00:05:26,390
Have some tea.

99
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,320
All right, Qiao.

100
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:34,830
I do miss the tea

101
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,080
we serve in the family.

102
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:37,230
Did the Lin family

103
00:05:37,230 --> 00:05:38,560
dock your expenses for tea?

104
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:40,790
Aunt, what are you talking about?

105
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,350
To the Lin family,

106
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,710
the tea we serve at home

107
00:05:43,909 --> 00:05:45,030
is rather uneconomical.

108
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,640
My mother-in-law is teaching me
how to handle the accounts.

109
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:49,000
I must set an example.

110
00:05:50,150 --> 00:05:51,320
Although the tea I chose

111
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:52,560
wasn't very expensive,

112
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:53,909
it has an exquisite taste.

113
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:55,590
Next time,

114
00:05:55,590 --> 00:05:57,000
I'll bring some back for you all.

115
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:59,520
Now that Pei has gotten married,

116
00:05:59,590 --> 00:06:01,120
she's really grown up.

117
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,230
Indeed.

118
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:03,200
She's looking the part now.

119
00:06:03,790 --> 00:06:04,880
My mother-in-law excels at needlework.

120
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:05,910
I've learned plenty of things from her.

121
00:06:05,910 --> 00:06:07,120
I embroidered
some small trinkets as well.

122
00:06:07,470 --> 00:06:09,150
I'll gift them to our elders later.

123
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,520
For the next few days,

124
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:12,390
both of you

125
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:13,120
shouldn't visit

126
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,200
your mother's place.

127
00:06:14,590 --> 00:06:16,120
Zhan has assumed his position
as an Imperial Insignia Guard.

128
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:17,710
They're upset about it.

129
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,710
If so, all the more reason
for visiting them.

130
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,710
I need to make our household proud.

131
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:24,790
Although I didn't marry into
a wealthy family,

132
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:27,560
my husband's career is flourishing.

133
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:28,680
He's nice to me too.

134
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:31,080
He was supposed to come back with me

135
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,350
if he didn't have

136
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:33,710
any official affairs to attend to.

137
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,150
Miss.

138
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:40,590
Your business is doing great.

139
00:06:43,590 --> 00:06:44,470
None of your business.

140
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,120
This street has never been safe.

141
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,590
You're only able
to do your business in peace

142
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,440
because of

143
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,270
our protection.

144
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,880
You see,

145
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:55,790
don't you think you need
to express your gratitude somehow?

146
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:56,560
Precisely.

147
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:57,440
Wait.

148
00:06:57,830 --> 00:06:58,350
He...

149
00:06:58,590 --> 00:06:59,150
It's fine.

150
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,790
The streets aren't safe

151
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,590
all thanks to you people.

152
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,080
You!

153
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:07,710
Thirty copper coins every month.

154
00:07:07,710 --> 00:07:08,910
Will you pay us or not?

155
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:10,830
Fine. I'll pay.

156
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,710
Hey buddy!

157
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,230
How dare you?

158
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,960
Wretch! I'll kill you!

159
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:23,680
How dare you cause trouble
in front of an Imperial Insignia Guard?

160
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,120
Imperial Insignia Guard?

161
00:07:24,350 --> 00:07:25,680
Buddy, he's one of them!

162
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:27,320
You...

163
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:29,120
You should be fulfilling your duty
in the imperial city.

164
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,710
Why are you here?

165
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:33,150
You tried to bully the weak
and extort money from them.

166
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,390
Should I not interfere?

167
00:07:34,470 --> 00:07:36,440
You've threatened the order of society
with your actions.

168
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:37,440
Should I not interfere?

169
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,440
Or, do you need me

170
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,200
to get the Capital Administration Office
involved?

171
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:41,230
Scram!

172
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,680
- Excellent!
- Bravo!

173
00:07:43,710 --> 00:07:45,350
The Imperial Insignia Guards
are brilliant indeed!

174
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:46,520
Everything's fine now.

175
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,150
You all may resume your trade.

176
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,270
Jiang Zhan, you're something else now.

177
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,470
You've become eloquent

178
00:08:13,470 --> 00:08:14,760
ever since you assumed your position.

179
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:16,760
Haven't I been eloquent from the start?

180
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,350
It's so heavy.

181
00:08:24,710 --> 00:08:25,470
The golden hawk?

182
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:27,960
This is the exclusive emblem

183
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:28,960
of the Imperial Insignia Guards.

184
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:31,440
Do you know it?

185
00:08:35,350 --> 00:08:36,200
It's not that cool.

186
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,280
It's not as cool

187
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,510
as my dagger.

188
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,590
Jiang Zhan.

189
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,560
You just assumed your position,

190
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:45,680
yet you didn't go home.

191
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,510
Don't tell me

192
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,320
you came here just to show off.

193
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,080
I...

194
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:49,510
I...

195
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,280
I'm very busy, you know?

196
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,590
I was just

197
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:54,870
passing by.

198
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,280
Mr. Zhan!

199
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,160
I saw someone causing trouble.

200
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,470
Mr. Zhan!

201
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:00,080
You walked too fast.

202
00:09:00,470 --> 00:09:01,110
But our home

203
00:09:01,110 --> 00:09:02,280
isn't in this direction.

204
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:05,710
It isn't?

205
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,040
Goodness. I can't find my way home

206
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:10,160
after assuming my position.

207
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:11,350
Where should we head?

208
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,630
Hey! Your sword!

209
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:13,870
Aji, take it!

210
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,960
Greetings, Grandmother.

211
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,080
Zhan.

212
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,680
Come closer. Let me take a look.

213
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,870
You look great.

214
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:49,350
In our mansion,

215
00:09:49,350 --> 00:09:50,680
you have the lousiest grades,

216
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:53,110
and you're the most disobedient

217
00:09:53,230 --> 00:09:53,990
and most mischievous

218
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:55,400
among all the kids.

219
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:58,080
You're inferior to your brother, Cang.

220
00:09:58,350 --> 00:10:00,870
Mother, how is that a compliment?

221
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,830
But no one would've expected you

222
00:10:02,990 --> 00:10:05,710
to bring the most honor

223
00:10:05,710 --> 00:10:06,440
to the family.

224
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,750
Grandmother, I have something to say.

225
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,080
When we reported for duty,

226
00:10:11,110 --> 00:10:12,350
we had plenty of members there.

227
00:10:12,710 --> 00:10:14,280
But Mr. Cui, our commander,

228
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,350
chose me

229
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,800
to serve His Majesty
for the Mid-Autumn Hunt.

230
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:20,280
Which Mr. Cui?

231
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:21,400
Cui Xu?

232
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:23,160
That's right. Do you know him?

233
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,680
Zhan, you've finally
made a name for yourself.

234
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:30,750
Come on.

235
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:33,400
Let's have a drink.

236
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:35,080
Ancheng,

237
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:38,160
Zhan just assumed his position.

238
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:39,440
You should at least

239
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,230
wait until Mother finishes

240
00:10:41,230 --> 00:10:42,280
her words.

241
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,680
Forget it. Just let them be.

242
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:46,560
Zhan,

243
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:49,320
listen up.

244
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,710
Now that you're
an Imperial Insignia Guard,

245
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,510
you must fulfill your duties.

246
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,510
You were designated by His Majesty.

247
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,830
You must perform your duties

248
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:57,040
better than anyone else

249
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,830
so that you won't let His Majesty down.

250
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,680
Yes, Grandmother!

251
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,200
Mother, we shall make a move first.

252
00:11:06,110 --> 00:11:06,510
Let's go.

253
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,960
Tell Yi and Si to join us.

254
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:16,200
Let's celebrate the occasion

255
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:18,160
as a family.

256
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,280
Sure.

257
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:20,440
I want to invite Yu as well.

258
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,110
Look at that smug attitude.

259
00:11:25,470 --> 00:11:27,750
I wasn't just saying that

260
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:29,830
for Zhan to listen.

261
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:33,160
It was also meant to encourage you.

262
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,800
Ancheng didn't make a name for himself.

263
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:37,870
But now,

264
00:11:37,990 --> 00:11:39,590
they're getting better and better.

265
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,160
The second branch

266
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:43,080
needs to put in more effort now.

267
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,470
Then our family

268
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:46,590
will flourish!

269
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:48,200
Yes, Mother.

270
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,160
Yes, Mother.

271
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,960
All right. You may leave.

272
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,320
Anmou.

273
00:11:59,110 --> 00:12:00,560
Anmou, don't be dejected.

274
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:02,710
Jiang Zhan is nothing.

275
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:04,110
At best,

276
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,630
he's
just a low-ranking military official.

277
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,870
Unlike our eldest son, Cang.

278
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,630
He's a properly educated

279
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:10,800
individual.

280
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,280
He may be

281
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,590
a low-ranking magistrate now,

282
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:14,630
but he'll be transferred
back to Ling'an City

283
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:15,680
in two years.

284
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:17,280
He'll have a bright future ahead of him.

285
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:18,800
So what if he's
an Imperial Insignia Guard?

286
00:12:18,830 --> 00:12:19,630
Enough!

287
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:27,280
