398
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:42,360
Aunt, help me out.

399
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:43,710
All right.

400
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:46,160
Tell me

401
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:47,470
