00:17:59,600 --> 00:18:00,160
No.

407
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:01,640
This won't do.

408
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:02,680
Why don't I send my men

409
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,400
