410
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,600
No! I don't want to get married!

411
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:05,960
There's nothing to inquire about.

412
00:18:06,230 --> 00:18:06,990
She just wants you

413
00:18:06,990 --> 00:18:07,960
to marry into a higher status

414
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:09,680
so that she can compete
with Zhan's success and please Anmou.

415
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:11,310
Qiao,

416
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,400
I haven't asked you

417
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:15,120
about your ideal marriage yet.

418
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,310
What kind of husband

419
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:17,200
are you looking for?

420
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:21,640
I don't want

421
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,640
to be married to a stranger.

422
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:26,550
I want to be married to someone I love.

423
00:18:30,990 --> 00:18:32,230
Qiao, I hope
that your wish will come true.

424
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,470
What exactly should I do?

425
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:38,640
Don't worry.

426
00:18:39,470 --> 00:18:40,840
I'll come up with a solution for you.

427
00:18:49,030 --> 00:18:50,070
- Excellent!
- Bravo!

