The secret tunnel is very complex.

429
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:56,990
It's filled with traps and dangers.

430
00:18:56,990 --> 00:18:58,600
One will perish

431
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,550
if they lose focus even for a second.

432
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:02,270
Li Qingyun relied on

433
00:19:02,270 --> 00:19:04,200
his exceptional courage and wisdom

434
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:06,310
to conquer one trap after another.

435
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:09,030
Lastly, at the end of the secret tunnel,

436
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:10,510
he found a...

