00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,790
He's different after becoming
an Imperial Insignia Guard.

441
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:22,070
- Indeed.
- That's right.

442
00:19:22,470 --> 00:19:23,400
Come on.

443
00:19:23,990 --> 00:19:26,070
Let's congratulate my son

444
00:19:26,120 --> 00:19:27,550
