457
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:55,270
Jiang, may you stay safe.

458
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:57,230
Now, you're an Imperial Insignia Guard.

459
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,990
Although you don't need
to go to the battlefield,

460
00:19:59,310 --> 00:20:01,470
