00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:14,030
Commandant Yu has a point.

468
00:20:14,230 --> 00:20:15,360
I've made

469
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:16,160
a protective pouch

470
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,200
for Zhan.

471
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:18,750
Zhan, may you stay safe
and free from worries.

472
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:20,840
Yi, I'm a grown-up now.

473
