482
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:37,230
Zhan, may you always return safely

483
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:39,310
from your duties.

484
00:20:40,070 --> 00:20:40,510
All right.

485
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:42,750
I can't keep up the pretense.

486
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:43,990
I like them so much.

487
00:20:43,990 --> 00:20:44,840
Thank you all so much.

488
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:46,360
This is great.

489
00:20:46,990 --> 00:20:48,440
Pei, welcome home.

490
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:51,790
Here.

491
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:53,120
Here. Try this.

492
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:54,640
Thank you, Father.

