00:20:58,230 --> 00:20:59,400
Qiao, why aren't you eating?

494
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,200
Perhaps she has no appetite.

495
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:04,840
Qiao, maybe just a few bites?

496
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:08,160
Qiao, if you're not enjoying the food,

497
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:11,120
