the family of Lingbei's governor.

505
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,840
Lingbei's governor?

506
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:40,310
He

507
00:21:40,310 --> 00:21:41,360
has a great reputation.

508
00:21:42,270 --> 00:21:44,710
And, his ancestors had rendered
military merits in the past.

509
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:46,960
Wouldn't it be great

510
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:50,710
