I asked someone to look into it.

512
00:21:53,790 --> 00:21:54,750
It is supposed to be Xiao Lang,

513
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:55,710
the second son of the official wife.

514
00:21:55,990 --> 00:21:57,600
