515
00:21:57,840 --> 00:21:59,270
He's a sickly man.

516
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:04,400
I've heard of that before.

517
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:08,710
The Xiao family has a son
who possesses powerful might.

518
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:09,920
It's a shame

519
00:22:10,030 --> 00:22:11,960
that he was left
with a chronic condition.

520
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:13,550
He never went on the battlefield

521
00:22:13,550 --> 00:22:14,440
since then.

522
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:16,230
Seems like we're referring

523
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:19,160
to that man.

524
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:20,510
Anmou.

525
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:23,400
All these years,

526
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:23,960
I've never made a plea

527
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:25,200
in front of you.

528
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:27,120
You brought me to your family,

529
00:22:27,270 --> 00:22:28,550
kept me well-dressed and well-fed,

530
00:22:28,710 --> 00:22:29,640
and provided me with a home.

531
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:33,470
But I only have two daughters.

532
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:35,030
I can't just let Qiao

533
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,270
be married to a sickly man.

534
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:38,840
You shouldn't say that.

535
00:22:39,230 --> 00:22:41,750
Mr. Xiao served the country
to the best of his abilities.

536
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:43,310
He has established

537
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:44,880
a good reputation.

538
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,030
But Qiao

539
00:22:46,030 --> 00:22:47,790
