540
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,230
No woman in the world

541
00:22:49,230 --> 00:22:50,750
is willing to be married
to a sickly man.

542
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:53,120
Qiao was pampered by Old Madam and you

543
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:54,550
