547
00:23:05,310 --> 00:23:06,120
Anmou!

548
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:22,310
Qiao, what do you think?

549
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:36,470
Father.

550
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:40,070
Can you please not chase me out?

551
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:44,550
I don't wish to get married yet.

552
00:24:04,710 --> 00:24:05,360
All right.

553
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,880
Understood.

554
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:22,550
Today's a joyous day indeed.

555
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:25,400
Even the moon looks bigger tonight.

556
00:24:27,710 --> 00:24:28,960
If only this moment

557
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:29,440
could last forever.

558
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:31,790
If only I could have a scented pouch

559
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:32,550
called Yangui.

560
00:24:33,920 --> 00:24:34,790
Mr. Yu, we see each other

561
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:36,070
