563
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:40,200
I came from Yangui City.

564
00:24:41,030 --> 00:24:42,030
It

565
00:24:42,030 --> 00:24:43,200
might be a remote border town,

566
00:24:43,510 --> 00:24:45,360
but it's busy in its own way,

567
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:46,840
and the people there
enjoy a peaceful life.

568
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,030
I love

569
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:49,310
