00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,120
The marriages of our children

668
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:22,600
are my responsibility.

669
00:29:24,990 --> 00:29:27,120
You've always been decisive
with your words.

670
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:30,510
But we shouldn't break the rules.

671
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:32,550
We can't afford to embarrass

672
00:29:32,710 --> 00:29:33,470
the Count of Dongping's Mansion

673
00:29:33,470 --> 00:29:35,120
for the sake of a concubine's daughter.

674
00:29:38,030 --> 00:29:39,790
Why complicate things?

675
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:41,840
Is there nothing new

676
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:43,070
in Ling'an City?

677
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:44,640
Are all of them

678
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:46,200
keeping an eye on my daughters?

679
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:47,120
Besides,

680
00:29:47,710 --> 00:29:48,550
Pei's mother

