00:29:48,550 --> 00:29:49,640
arranged the marriage for her too.

682
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:50,790
Look at

683
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:52,710
how well she's doing now.

684
00:29:53,990 --> 00:29:54,600
If you want to blame someone,

685
00:29:56,070 --> 00:29:57,710
you should blame yourself
for finding the wrong candidate.

686
00:29:57,990 --> 00:29:58,510
For Pei,

687
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:00,360
I wanted to betroth her

688
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:02,510
to Mr. Zhen Heng
of the Capital Administration Office.

689
00:30:03,120 --> 00:30:05,230
But they took advantage of the situation

690
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:06,200
and married her off

691
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:07,400
while I was sick.

692
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,470
Anmou,

693
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:13,070
you should listen

694
00:30:13,510 --> 00:30:15,750
to both sides of the story.

695
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,920
Qiao is the third eldest girl

696
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,600
in the family.

697
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,440
She's no longer young.

698
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:23,030
Besides, she is

699
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:25,270
shy and quiet.

700
00:30:25,270 --> 00:30:26,120
Bringing her out

701
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:27,960
is like bringing someone
who's always in her shell.

702
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:29,440
Arranging a marriage for her

703
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:31,550
is no easy feat.

704
00:30:32,470 --> 00:30:33,230
In addition,

705
00:30:33,510 --> 00:30:34,990
our family's reputation

706
00:30:34,990 --> 00:30:36,600
has deteriorated over the years.

707
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:39,600
Jiang Si insisted on
annulling her marriage before this.

708
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,160
The entire Ling'an City

709
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:43,200
has heard about it.

710
00:30:43,230 --> 00:30:45,120
Isn't it embarrassing enough?

711
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:47,600
Do you want the daughters of our branch

712
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,440
to imitate her?

713
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,200
Dear.

714
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:56,160
You're a mother yourself.

715
00:30:56,360 --> 00:30:57,750
No matter how good Mr. Xiao is,

716
00:30:57,750 --> 00:30:59,160
you should search your conscience.

717
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:00,990
Is he truly a good candidate

718
00:31:00,990 --> 00:31:02,750
as a husband?

719
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:03,510
Mr. Xiao

720
00:31:03,510 --> 00:31:05,160
