00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:23,510
You held a grudge
against Madam Ruan all these years.

731
00:31:23,960 --> 00:31:25,550
But even if you wish to vent your anger,

732
00:31:25,550 --> 00:31:26,230
you shouldn't vent it

733
00:31:26,230 --> 00:31:27,200
on my child.

734
00:31:29,310 --> 00:31:29,960
Anmou.

735
00:31:30,990 --> 00:31:32,710
Why would there

736
00:31:32,710 --> 00:31:34,230
be a grudge between me and Madam Ruan?

