00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:35,960
Why would I vent my anger

738
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:37,510
on the children?

739
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:41,840
Anmou.

740
00:31:42,360 --> 00:31:43,990
I'm doing this for your sake.

741
00:31:44,750 --> 00:31:46,550
I'm trying to bring honor to our branch.

742
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:48,470
When Zhan left Mother's room

743
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:50,230
after he assumed his position,

744
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:51,400
other people might not know

745
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,510
what you were thinking,

746
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:54,070
but I knew what was on your mind.

747
00:31:54,070 --> 00:31:55,160
Stop it!

748
00:31:55,230 --> 00:31:56,360
I've never seen

749
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:58,160
a female head

