00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:07,360
Dear.

756
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:08,960
Not everyone

757
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:09,960
is a pawn.

758
00:32:10,710 --> 00:32:11,160
I suppose

