00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,600
Qian left you
because of this very reason.

760
00:32:17,790 --> 00:32:18,710
What a shame.

761
00:32:20,470 --> 00:32:22,270
Anmou, you're one step too late.

762
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:24,510
What do you mean?

