00:32:24,710 --> 00:32:25,920
I've already accepted

764
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:27,230
the Xiao family's invitation.

765
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,920
I've delivered the letter.

766
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:30,200
And, I've affixed it

767
00:32:30,230 --> 00:32:32,200
